<item>
            <title>[LU-4952] osd_declare_write_commit may give wrong offset &amp; size to dmu_tx_hold_write</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4952</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in osd_declare_write_commit():&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;       for (i = 0; i &amp;lt; npages; i++) {
            ......
            dmu_tx_hold_write(oh-&amp;gt;ot_tx, obj-&amp;gt;oo_db-&amp;gt;db_object, offset, size);
            space += osd_count_not_mapped(obj, offset, size);

            offset = lnb-&amp;gt;lnb_file_offset;
            size = lnb-&amp;gt;len;
       }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;they should be lnb&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;i&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.lnb_file_offset and lnb&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;i&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.len.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
